_sText:
The classic nuke, with CSGO's layout!

Or rather... A rough approximation of it.

Warning!

Not everything is exactly as it was on GO, which is to be expected but still, some things may not look right.

Either because of a botched decompile (in which it has been through a couple) or just a misplaced object... Who knows? Who cares? If i didn't see it; i just pray that no one else does too. (kliks said that!)

Though if you have some suggestions, or things I've missed to warrant a comment, say it.

This is not really for competitive play, but if you want to you definitely can.

This is a vanity project to see what it would look like to use Half-Life and 1.6's assets and maps, then make it like the new ones. (also because I have a subpar computer and just wanted to play casually with my friends on this map without any big frame dips)

Enjoy.
